ComicInfo.Summary:
After going through the wringer with the Avengers, Jennifer Walters--known to many as SHE-HULK--decided to return to civilian life. She rejoined her former boss, MALLORY BOOK, at her law firm and regained access to her former residence, a penthouse apartment owned by Janet Van Dyne, the WASP. With her old job and her old wardrobe, everything was coming up Jen.
That is, until someone unexpected crasher back into her life. JACK OF HEARTS was a friend and fellow Avenger--a half-alien, half-human super hero with the powers of a nuclear reactor. Jen thought he was dead. So why is he lying in the middle of her floor?
ComicInfo.Title: Jen, Again, Part 2
